1956;;The Secret Tent;;British;;Don Chaffey;;Donald Gray, Andree Melly;;crime;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Secret_Tent;;Respectable wife Ruth attempts to conceal her secret past as a criminal from neighbours and from her husband Chris. However, when a neighbour is burgled and Ruth mysteriously disappears, she becomes the police's prime suspect. Husband Chris searches the city for Ruth, in hopes of proving her innocence.